    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588310/extras/3fa20a0b7b68f71580ff3ab83f1bb981.avif?t=1770460019\" width=1560 height=613 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this 2D puzzle-platforming metroidvania, play as Little Ghost, navigating an inch-high little lady through an interconnected collage landscape. Interact with scattered office supplies and unique characters, collect media and art, traverse a vast map of perilous office furniture and décor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588310/extras/95f51271d7dd96e6482300318da97433.avif?t=1770460019\" width=1286 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full game release Fall 2026 || Our 2022 Kickstarter Demo is still available for the enthused. More than a sneak peek, you can access 2-3hours worth of early game play today!  We even made demo-specific Steam achievements! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588310/extras/d6a9e7e00495b2d358d6d41c0167b79a.avif?t=1770460019\" width=1560 height=544 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the scattered world of a wind blown office space; a peculiar sketchbook, grand bookshelf, and labyrinthine computer stretch out before you as you uncover truths and recover lost memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize retro-inspired platforming, including familiar move sets such as grappling hook and super-dash, and introducing a unique ~float~ mechanic, in lieu of combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unveil the secrets of Prime Products Division, the mysterious corporation manufacturing the abundance of goods and resources you know and trust</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet animated physical and digital characters come to life as you navigate the gorgeous, the strange, the absurd, and the uncanny</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquaint yourself with eclectic practitioners of the occult who direct or distract from your quest, granting power-ups and challenging your knowledge and perception</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain enemies-turned-allies as new playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mixed media along the way to set your own in-game vibes, including a large library of musical tracks and podcasts, all organized on a Tamagachi-like interface</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shuffle the deck of chance and destiny as you gather and glean tarot card wisdom and insights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a breathtaking, single-contiguous collage full of secret hidden spaces within a non-linear, unlockable map</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588310/extras/246741e84b4736c837ff32322de45f14.avif?t=1770460019\" width=1560 height=538 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588310/extras/175b52cc34666a259d73f170fbde1475.avif?t=1770460019\" width=1560 height=538 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Streamers have our permission to broadcast the Little Ghost music &amp; podcasts on their streams and playthrus.</i></strong></p>",
